to.name: Mt Hood Ave MAX Station Shuttle Stop

alerts.alertDescriptionText: Service has been suspended on this route due to dangerous conditions.

Due to dangerous conditions, bus, MAX service is limited. LIFT Paratransit has been suspended. Check trimet.org/alerts for the latest updates. TriMet Customer Service is operating with limited capacity through Twitter and text. Portland Streetcar service has been suspended. Please avoid travel until weather and road conditions improve.  Federal law requires riders to wear a mask or face covering. Dress warmly and use extra caution when boarding trains and buses and around transit centers.

MAX Red Line service disrupted due to winter weather. Shuttle buses serving between Gateway TC to PDX. Board MAX Blue Line for service between Rose Quarter TC and Gateway TC.
